      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=fhontdmny7]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=fhontdmny7]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bd67kl9ykt]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bd67kl9ykt]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=wr6cwdtpym]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=wr6cwdtpym]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608337987/Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758275256266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608337987/Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758275256266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"563\" data-width=\"1200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608010341\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608337987\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"3e0d53a6-5398-4cfe-a5b1-3549902a2b86\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608337987/Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758275256266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=563 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608337987/Stylized-Looks-Shipshape-docs.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758275256266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"fhontdmny7\">Project</span></strong>: Ship Shape</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"bd67kl9ykt\">Created by</span></strong>:  Ernst Janssen Groesbeek <br />of&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.9to3animation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>9 to 3 Animation</u></a>.</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"wr6cwdtpym\">Features</span></strong>: Stylized Looks</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Ship concept by Ian McQue.</p><p>Robot concept by Ruslan Safarov.</p><p>Models by Cheyenne Chapel, Aliya Chen, Damian Kwiatkowski, Alyssa Minko, Anthony Muscarella, and Miguel Zozaya</p><p>&copy; Disney/Pixar - RenderMan &quot;Shipshape&quot; Art Challenge</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/renderman-examples/R26/RfM/Shipshape_RfM.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"36505171-0bea-4265-9dbf-ae01b8da13ea.png\" width=\"286\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608337987/36505171-0bea-4265-9dbf-ae01b8da13ea.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758269783504&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286